edu.udel.cis.taschd.course

Class CourseInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.udel.cis.taschd.course.CourseInstance

  • public class CourseInstance
extends java.lang.Object

    The CourseInstance represents an instance of a Course within a given term or semester. A Course does not keep same for every term. Given that, CourseInstances instantiate when a given course is being offered. Examples include Fall 2018 CISC 675 which is a CourseInstance of the CISC 675 Course.

    CourseInstance is an instance of a Course, which contains all courses in the university.
